                                  bsp-extras
                                  ----------

1. Introduction
----------------

The bsp-extras template will install some useful but not always
required tools define by BSP_EXTRA_PACKAGES in bsp layer.

2. Usage
--------

Add this template to your configure line to enable it:
 --templates feature/bsp-extras

3. Installation
----------------

This template will include some useful tools in the root filesystem.
You can get the extra tools list in variable BSP_EXTRAS_PACKAGES
by looking at the output of the bitbake -e command.

#@TYPE: Wrtemplate
#@NAME: bsp-extras
#@DESCRIPTION: Enable BSP extras packages support
